#CSS
body, html {
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column; /* Aligns items vertically */
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    
    
}

